note.note: A project-specific code has been created in order to study the phenomen of liaison in French. A full description of this code is available in the documentation file accompanying the corpus.

setting.activity: This recording takes place at the family's home, at Clermont-Ferrand, and more precisely in the child's bedroom. The father and his daughter play various role-playing games (the father and the mother, the waitress and the cook). Then, they look at some picture books and the father reads some books to the child.
